<h4 id="raii">RAII</h4>

<h4 id="layout">Layout</h4>
<ol>
  <li>Initilized data segment: all the global &amp; static variables that were
initialized to a non-zero values, and all constant data, are stored here.</li>
  <li>Uninitalized data segment(BSS): All the global and static variables that were
either not initialized, or initialized to zero, are stored in this segment.</li>
</ol>

